# Web design showcase pattern

Every new design must ship **both** a live interactive demo and a landing-page preview. Do not ship OG/static thumbnail-only cards on the home page.

Reference implementation: **Art** (`id: art`).

## 1. Catalog entry

Add to `designs` in [`lib/data.ts`](lib/data.ts):

- `id` — kebab-case slug (e.g. `art`)
- `demoPath` — always `/designs/<id>`
- `image` — still used on `/designs` catalog cards
- `title`, `description`, `tags`, `price`, `category`, optional `featured`

## 2. Live demo at `/designs/<id>`

Mirror Art’s host pattern:

| Piece | Path |
|-------|------|
| Showcase shell | `app/designs/<id>/layout.tsx` |
| App routes | `app/designs/<id>/…` (pages, nested layouts) |
| Design UI | `components/<id>/…` |
| Design tokens / CSS | e.g. `app/designs/<id>/<id>.css` (import from globals if needed) |

Requirements:

- Wrap the design in [`ProductFrame`](components/product-frame.tsx) (window chrome + title like `designs/<id>`)
- Real navigation and interaction inside the frame
- Keep the design self-contained (own fonts/tokens under a root class, e.g. `art-root`)
- Do **not** iframe the live app on the landing page

## 3. Landing showcase + inert preview

Home Web Designs section is a **1/3 intro + 2/3 ProductFrame preview** ([`components/landing/designs-showcase.tsx`](components/landing/designs-showcase.tsx)), not an OG card grid.

For each featured design:

1. **Inert mock** — `components/landing/<id>-preview-mock.tsx`
   - Visually match the live home (header + main composition)
   - Hardcoded sample copy; no design routing, i18n providers, or data fetches
   - Autoplay / CSS motion OK; **clicks must do nothing** (`inert` / no real links)
   - `role="img"` + accessible name (e.g. “Art design preview”)
2. **Wire into showcase** — extend `DesignsShowcase` (or a shared multi-design section) so the left column reads from `lib/data.ts` and the right column renders the mock inside `ProductFrame`
3. Load that design’s fonts on the preview wrapper the same way the live layout does

Only left-column CTAs navigate (`Open live demo` → `demoPath`, `View all` → `/designs`).

## 4. Do / don’t

```text
✅ Live app at /designs/<id> inside ProductFrame
✅ Landing: copy + inert mock preview
✅ Catalog /designs may keep static image cards

❌ Landing OG/static cards as the only “showcase”
❌ Embedding the live route via iframe on the home page
❌ Importing live HomeBento / SiteHeader (or equivalents) into the landing mock
❌ Clickable navigation inside the landing preview
```

## Checklist for a new design

- [ ] `lib/data.ts` entry with `demoPath: '/designs/<id>'`
- [ ] `app/designs/<id>/` live demo + `ProductFrame`
- [ ] `components/landing/<id>-preview-mock.tsx` (inert)
- [ ] Landing showcase shows intro + preview (not OG-only)
- [ ] `/designs` catalog card still works with `image` + `demoPath`
